<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <!-- Meta tags obrigatórias -->
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport"
          content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, shrink-to-fit=no" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <title>@ViewBag.Title - Originários</title>

    <!-- Título -->
    <title>Originários</title>

    <!-- Ícone -->
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="./images/favico3.png" type="image/x-icon" />

    <!-- CSS only -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    @Styles.Render("~/Content/css")

</head>

<body class="text-light">
    <!---------- início div principal ---------->
    <div id="divPrincipal" class="row">
        <div class="col-12 container-fluid d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
            <!---------- início nav ---------->
            <nav class="row p-none">
                <div id="nav" class="col-6 col-lg-8 navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-transparent ">
                    <div class="container-fluid justify-content-start">
                        <button class="navbar-toggler my-2 my-lg-0" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navToggler" aria-controls="navToggler" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Menu de navegação">
                            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                        </button>
                        <a class="navbar-brand text-light mx-2 mx-sm-4 me-auto" href="javascript:void(0)">Logo</a>
                        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navToggler">
                            <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-lg-0">
                                <li class="nav-item">
                                    @Html.ActionLink("Home", "Index", "Home", null, htmlAttributes: new { @class = "nav-link px-4 py-3" })
                                </li>
                                <li class="nav-item">
                                    @Html.ActionLink("Produtos", "Index", "Produtos", null, htmlAttributes: new { @class = "nav-link px-4 py-3" })
                                </li>
                                <li class="nav-item">
                                    @Html.ActionLink("Contato", "Contact", "Home", null, htmlAttributes: new { @class = "nav-link px-4 py-3" })
                                </li>

                                @if (Request.IsAuthenticated)
                                {
                                    <li class="nav-item">
                                        @Html.ActionLink("Meus Produtos", "Index", "Postagens", null, htmlAttributes: new { @class = "nav-link px-4 py-3" })
                                    </li>
                                }
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6 col-lg-4 navbar-light d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                    @Html.Partial("_LoginPartial")
                </div>
            </nav>
            <!---------- fim nav ---------->
            <!---------- início main ---------->
            <main class="row">
                <!---------- início conteudo central ---------->
                <div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8 mx-auto p-4 px-md-0">
                    @RenderBody()
                    @*<p>
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut mattis,
                        elit non maximus imperdiet, magna eros luctus massa, et iaculis nibh
                        dui at erat. Duis sit amet lacus rutrum, blandit lorem ac, hendrerit
                        enim. Proin eu dignissim nulla, at commodo nisi. Ut dapibus luctus
                        libero ised, fringilla massa. Phasellus id tristique
                        nunc. Praesent metus magna, lacinia eu nibh a, commodo rutrum nisl.
                        Ut eget massa sem. Morbi imperdiet non mauris non rhoncus. In
                        porttitor blandit sapien, molestie tempor felis egestas ac. Nunc eu
                        justo augue. Integer sodales volutpat ante, at mattis diam iaculis
                        placerat. Praesent a tellus quis orci imperdiet sollicitudin vel sed
                        mi.
                    </p>
                    <br />*@
                </div>
                <!---------- fim conteudo central ---------->

            </main>
            <!---------- fim main ---------->
            <!---------- início footer ---------->
            <footer class="row text-light p-3">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-center">
                    <p class="">&copy; @DateTime.Now.Year - Originários</p>
                    <p>Recode Pro - 2021</p>
                    <p>Projeto Final - Squad41</p>
                    <address>
                        <span>Contato:</span> <a class="text-light" href="mailto:squad41recode@gmail.com">squad41recode@gmail.com</a>
                    </address>
                </div>

                <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-center">
                    <p class="mb-2"><strong>Desenvolvedores:</strong></p>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled pt-none">
                        <li>Amanda...</li>
                        <li>Andryele...</li>
                        <li>Carla...</li>
                        <li>Diego...</li>
                        <li>John Michael...</li>
                        <li>Vítor Mateus Santos Parreiras</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </footer>
            <!---------- fim footer ---------->
        </div>
    </div>
    <!---------- fim div principal ---------->

    <!-- JavaScript -->
    @*@Scripts.Render("~/bundles/jquery")*@
    @RenderSection("scripts", required: false)

    <!-- JavaScript Bundle with Popper -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
